        <updateDate>2020-10-26T19:36:37Z</updateDate>
        <text><![CDATA[ <p><b>FHA Foreclosure Prevention Act of 2019</b></p> <p>This bill revises foreclosure-prevention measures for single-family homes insured by the Federal Housing Administration. Specifically, the bill </p> <ul> <li>requires documentation from mortgage servicers of loss mitigation efforts, </li> <li>provides the Department of Housing and Urban Development with oversight responsibilities over mortgage servicers,</li> <li>establishes a complaint procedure for borrowers regarding mortgage servicers, and</li> <li>requires a mortgage servicer to provide notice to borrowers regarding the loss mitigation process. </li> </ul>]]></text>
      </summary>
    </summaries>
